### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Rishabh Burman",
    "email": "rishabh@gmail.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "rishabh@gmail.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Try accessing protected endpoint without token (should get 401/403)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses

### Create an expense
POST http://localhost:8080/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJyaXNoYWJoQGdtYWlsLmNvbSIsImlhdCI6MTc3ODE1NDg2OCwiZXhwIjoxNzc4MjQxMjY4fQ.qK2iqfP1CT8NjPfxabKlWUPCGZbSj4LMG9M2lHDqn5v_ok5-UZ8-OIjBJ6vuB8aYXrUU5p1WoBBTQF51oeRbew

{
    "title": "Swiggy dinner",
    "amount": 450.00,
    "category": "FOOD",
    "expenseDate": "2026-05-07",
    "note": "Biryani"
}

