### Try registering with same email (should get 400 - duplicate email)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Rishabh Burman",
    "email": "rishabh@gmail.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Try login with wrong password (should get 401)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "rishabh@gmail.com",
    "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### Try registering with invalid data (should get 400 with field errors)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "",
    "email": "notanemail",
    "password": "abc"
}

